In the devices I make I call them all Boot ROMs. Firmware term I have never really used and BIOS I consider something useful to the programs running on the machine past boot. Boot ROM still covers all the starting up aspects.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3483">TmEE</a> — Fri Apr 19, 2013 8:42 pm</p><hr />
